<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Informational message:  Increased Error Rates and Latencies>
We are investigating increased error rates and latencies for API calls and the IAM Management Console.

<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Service is operating normally: [RESOLVED]  Increased Error Rates and Latencies>
Between 3:10 PM and 3:34 PM PDT we experienced increased error rates and latencies for API calls and the IAM Management Console. The issue has been resolved and the service is operating normally.
